description: Use Extract Video Info for social-video text and fact extraction.
globs:
alwaysApply: false
---

When a task asks for visible text, captions, OCR hints, named entities, books, products, ratings, or timestamps from Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, or local videos, follow `skills/extract-video-info/SKILL.md`.

For user-facing install instructions, use `docs/agent-install-prompts.md`.

Prefer the Python CLI from the repository root:

```bash
python -m extract_video_info "<video-url-or-path>" --outdir work/video-evidence --fps 1
```

Do not duplicate the skill workflow in this rule; update the canonical `SKILL.md` instead.
